command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.CreateUoM
command.description: Creates a new Unit of Measure.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.DeleteUoM
command.description: Deletes an existing Unit of Measure.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UpdateUoM
command.description: Updates a Unit of Measure.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.CreateUoMFactor
command.description: Creates a new UoM Factor which defines the conversion between a source Unit of Measure and a target Unit of Measure.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UpdateUoMFactor
command.description: Updates a UoM Factor.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.DeleteUoMFactor
command.description: Deletes an existing UoM Factor.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.HideUoM
command.description: Hides the specified Unit of Measure (UoM), and in case of a base UoM, also all its related UoMs and UoM Factors by setting the attribute IsHidden to True.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.CreateStateMachine
command.description: Creates a new State Machine.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UpdateStateMachine
command.description: Updates the name and/or description of the specified State Machine.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.HideStateMachine
command.description: Hides the specified State Machine and all the Statuses and the State Transitions related to that State Machine by setting the attribute IsHidden to True.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UnhideStateMachine
command.description: Unhides the specified State Machine, all the Statuses and the State Transitions related to that State Machine by setting the attribute IsHidden to False.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.DeleteStateMachine
command.description: Deletes an existing State Machine.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.FreezeStateMachine
command.description: Configures the State Machine to be read-only by setting the attribute IsFrozen to True.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UnfreezeStateMachine
command.description: Removes the read-only setting from the State Machine by setting the attribute IsFrozen to False.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.CreateStatus
command.description: Creates a new Status.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UnhideUoM
command.description: Unhides the specified Unit of Measure and the related UoM Dimension by setting the attribute IsHidden to False. In case of a base UoM, the IsHidden setting is also removed from the UoM Factors defined between the base UoM and the other base UoMs not hidden. In case of a multiple/submultiple UoM, the IsHidden setting is also removed from the related base UoM, if hidden.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.DeleteStatus
command.description: Deletes an existing Status.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UpdateStatus
command.description: Updates the name and/or the description and/or the color of a Status.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.CreateStatusDefinition
command.description: Creates a new Status Definition.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UnhideStatusDefinition
command.description: Unhides a Status Definition by setting the attribute IsHidden to False.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.FreezeStatusDefinition
command.description: Configures theStatus Definition to be read-only by setting the attribute IsFrozen to True.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.HideStatusDefinition
command.description: Hides the Status Definition by setting the attribute IsHidden to True.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UnfreezeStatusDefinition
command.description: Removes the read-only setting from the Status Definition by setting the attribute IsFrozen to False.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.DeleteStatusDefinition
command.description: Deletes an existing Status Definition.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UpdateStatusDefinition
command.description: Updates the name and/or description and/or color of a Status Definition.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.CreateStatusTransition
command.description: Creates a new Status Transition, which defines an allowed status change within a specific lifecycle.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.DeleteStatusTransition
command.description: Deletes an existing Status Transition.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UpdateStatusTransition
command.description: Updates a Status Transition.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.ConvertQuantity
command.description: Converts a given quantity (value and UoM) into the corresponding quantity, expressed in the target UoM.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.CreateLocation
command.description: Creates a new Location. This command has been deprecated. Its functionalities are now provided by the CreateEquipmentConfiguration command (EQU_MS) and CreateEquipment command (EQU_OP).

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UpdateLocation
command.description: Updates the given Location. This command has been deprecated. Its functionalities are now provided by the UpdateEquipmentConfiguration command (EQU_MS) and UpdateEquipment command (EQU_OP).

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.DeleteLocation
command.description: Deletes an existing Location. This command has been deprecated. Its functionalities are now provided by the DeleteEquipmentConfiguration command (EQU_MS) and DeleteEquipment command (EQU_OP).

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.FreezeLocation
command.description: Configures the given Location to be read-only by setting the attribute IsFrozen to True. This command has been deprecated. Its functionalities are now provided by the FreezeEquipmentConfiguration command (EQU_MS) and FreezeEquipment command (EQU_OP).

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UnfreezeLocation
command.description: Removes the read-only setting from the given Location by setting the attribute IsFrozen to False. This command has been deprecated. Its functionalities are now provided by the UnfreezeEquipmentConfiguration command (EQU_MS) and UnfreezeEquipment command (EQU_OP).

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.HideLocation
command.description: Hides the given Location by setting the attribute IsHidden to True. This command has been deprecated.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UnhideLocation
command.description: Unhides the given Location by setting the attribute IsHidden to False. This command has been deprecated.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.CreateWorkCenter
command.description: Creates a new Work Center. This command has been deprecated. Its functionalities are now provided by the CreateEquipmentConfiguration command (EQU_MS) and CreateEquipment command (EQU_OP).

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UpdateWorkCenter
command.description: Updates an existing Work Center, optionally adding Wortk Center Items. This command has been deprecated. Its functionalities are now provided by the UpdateEquipmentConfiguration command (EQU_MS) and UpdateEquipment command (EQU_OP).

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.DeleteWorkCenter
command.description: Deletes an existing Work Center. This command has been deprecated. Its functionalities are now provided by the DeleteEquipmentConfiguration command (EQU_MS) and DeleteEquipment command (EQU_OP).

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.FreezeWorkCenter
command.description: Configures a Work Center to be read-only by setting the attribute IsFrozen to True. This command has been deprecated. Its functionalities are now provided by the FreezeEquipmentConfiguration command (EQU_MS) and FreezeEquipment command (EQU_OP).

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UnfreezeWorkCenter
command.description: Removes the read-only setting from a Work Center by setting the attribute IsFrozen to False. This command has been deprecated. Its functionalities are now provided by the UnfreezeEquipmentConfiguration command (EQU_MS) and UnfreezeEquipment command (EQU_OP).

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.HideWorkCenter
command.description: Hides the Work Center by setting the attribute IsHidden to True. This command has been deprecated.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UnhideWorkCenter
command.description: Unhides a Work Center by setting the attribute IsHidden to False. This command has been deprecated.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UpdateWorkCenterItem
command.description: Updates an existing Work Center Item. This command has been deprecated. Its functionalities are now provided by the DeleteEquipmentGraphLinkConfiguration, DeleteEquipmentGraphNodeConfiguration, CreateEquipmentGraphNodeConfiguration, CreateEquipmentGrapghLinkConfiguration commands (EQU_MS) and corresponding commands (EQU_OP).

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.DeleteWorkCenterItem
command.description: Deletes an existing Work Center Item. This command has been deprecated. Its functionalities are now provided by the DeleteEquipmentGraphLinkConfiguration, DeleteEquipmentGraphNodeConfiguration commands (EQU_MS) and DeleteEquipmentGraphLink, DeleteEquipmentGraphNode commands (EQU_OP).

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.HideWorkCenterItem
command.description: Hides the Work Center Item by setting the attribute IsHidden to True. This command has been deprecated.

command.name: Siemens.SimaticIT.ReferenceData.UDM_RF.RFModel.Commands.UnhideWorkCenterItem
command.description: Unhides a Work Center Item by setting the attribute IsHidden to False. This command has been deprecated.
